OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRoyal Mail prioritising    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fparcels over letters - MP  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Royal Mail has been accused by a senior
OL,6, MP of breaching its legal obligations  
OL,7, by prioritising parcels over letters.  
OL,9,FBusiness Committee chair Darren Jones  
OL,10,Fsaid a poster in a delivery office sent
OL,11,Fto him by a whistle-blower had told    
OL,12,Fworkers to favour delivering parcels.  
OL,14,FHe showed it to Royal Mail chief       
OL,15,Fexecutive Simon Thompson who was giving
OL,16,Fevidence to the committee.             
OL,18,FMr Thompson said he was aware of the   
OL,19,Fsign but that it was "absolutely not   
OL,20,Four policy".                           
